00:40:13.390 --> 00:40:14.400
now available in Carbon.

00:40:14.400 --> 00:40:19.350
So Carbon apps can deliver a real system
toolbar just like Mail or just like

00:40:19.350 --> 00:40:22.400
other Cocoa applications you've seen,
