00:46:40.880 --> 00:46:42.820
over here on the aquified interface.

00:46:42.820 --> 00:46:47.650
Another point that something different
that happened in Power Plant that

00:46:47.650 --> 00:46:52.510
some people have tripped up on is
when you use the static text control,

00:46:52.530 --> 00:46:55.680
the control manager automatically
erases to the background.

00:46:55.700 --> 00:47:00.210
In this case,
you get the gray striped background here.

00:47:00.320 --> 00:47:02.370
And if you're drawing
your text over a picture,

00:47:02.410 --> 00:47:04.040
well, you probably don't want that.

00:47:04.040 --> 00:47:06.720
What you want to use
is the theme text box.

00:47:06.740 --> 00:47:09.880
This still draws anti-alias text,
but it doesn't do the

00:47:09.880 --> 00:47:11.370
erase before you draw.

00:47:11.370 --> 00:47:12.210
So if you actually want to draw text,
you can do that by

00:47:12.210 --> 00:47:12.740
clicking on the text box.

00:47:12.740 --> 00:47:14.860
So if you're drawing your
text over a background,

00:47:14.860 --> 00:47:17.770
use the theme text drawing box
instead of a static text control.

00:47:17.780 --> 00:47:20.700
Another point here,
although it's not obvious visually,

00:47:20.820 --> 00:47:25.020
is something that Apple has recommended,
is that the title of your pop-up

00:47:25.020 --> 00:47:28.400
menu should actually not use the
title of the pop-up menu control.

00:47:28.500 --> 00:47:32.470
You should actually create your title
for the pop-up using a separate,

00:47:32.910 --> 00:47:35.860
either a static text control
or a theme text box drawing,

00:47:35.940 --> 00:47:37.410
so that the two are independent.

00:47:37.460 --> 00:47:42.650
It has to do with the
appearance and dimming,

00:47:42.660 --> 00:47:42.660
because if I actually
made this the title,

00:47:42.660 --> 00:47:47.160
it actually wouldn't dim here properly
when I deactivated the window.

00:47:47.160 --> 00:47:49.660
So that's just another quick tip
there to get your applications

00:47:49.660 --> 00:47:51.550
looking right on Aqua.

